title: 1.72 Flan’s mod 一放载具就闪退
author: Carlton
txt_content:
已安装mod如下：
Forge Mod Loader7.2.116.1024
Forge 10.12.0.1024
Render Player API 1.2
Minecraft Coder Pack8.09
Flansmod 4.2.3
MrClayfish Furniture mod 3.2.9。2
Village  Taverns 2.2.0
